              <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item faq-active">
                  <h3>
                    <span class="num">1.</span>
                    <span
                      >How does your furniture collection service work?</span
                    >
                  </h3>
                  <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>
                      Our collection service makes it easy for consumers and
                      businesses to responsibly dispose of unwanted furniture
                      and mattresses. Simply schedule a pickup through our platform,
                      and we'll ensure the items are collected dry making
                      it possible for them to be recycled with certified recyclers
                      or given a second life with NGOs.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <i class="faq-toggle bi bi-chevron-right"></i>
                </div>
                <!-- End Faq item-->

                <div class="faq-item">
                  <h3>
                    <span class="num">2.</span>
                    <span>What types of furniture do you refurbish?</span>
                  </h3>
                  <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>
                      We refurbish a wide range of items, including mattresses,
                      chairs, tables, and storage units. Our goal is to restore
                      these items to high-quality standards for resale to
                      budget-conscious and circular-minded consumers.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <i class="faq-toggle bi bi-chevron-right"></i>
                </div>
                <!-- End Faq item-->

                <div class="faq-item">
                  <h3>
                    <span class="num">3.</span>
                    <span
                      >How do you ensure sustainability in your processes?</span
                    >
                  </h3>
                  <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>
                      We partner with certified recyclers, furniture
                      refurbishments to extend its lifecycle, and use
                      data-driven tools like AI and blockchain to optimize
                      supply chains and minimize waste.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <i class="faq-toggle bi bi-chevron-right"></i>
                </div>
                <!-- End Faq item-->

                <div class="faq-item">
                  <h3>
                    <span class="num">4.</span>
                    <span>Who can benefit from your services?</span>
                  </h3>
                  <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>
                      Our services cater to individuals, businesses, housing
                      providers, and any organization seeking a convenient
                      solution for furniture disposal. We also offer tools for
                      tracking furniture lifecycles, reducing waste generation
                      and enhance transparency within the production process in
                      line with circular economy goals.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <i class="faq-toggle bi bi-chevron-right"></i>
                </div>
                <!-- End Faq item-->

                <div class="faq-item">
                  <h3>
                    <span class="num">5.</span>
                    <span>What does your data portal offer?</span>
