                  <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>
                      The data portal offers lifecycle analysis, supply chain
                      transparency, insights on alternative circular materials,
                      and compliance tools for manufacturers to meet EU
                      regulations and embrace sustainability.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <i class="faq-toggle bi bi-chevron-right"></i>
